                    <h2 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name">
                        诺奖黑历史：恐怖的“前脑叶白质切除术” 
                    </h2>
                    <div class="rich_media_meta_list">
                                                <span id="copyright_logo" class="rich_media_meta meta_original_tag">原创</span>
                        						                        <em id="post-date" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">2016-05-13</em>

                                                <em class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">鬼谷藏龙</em>
                                                <a class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_link rich_media_meta_nickname" href="javascript:void(0);" id="post-user">果壳网</a>
                        <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text rich_media_meta_nickname">果壳网</span>

                        <div id="js_profile_qrcode" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">
                            <div class="profile_inner">
                                <strong class="profile_nickname">果壳网</strong>
